1.title: Down Home Delicious

episode of.title: Poultry Princess Cooking with Schatar (TV Series 2018– )

1.plot: Schatar and Aunt Jeannine explore restaurants around the country to learn yummy secrets from top chefs. In this episode, Janie of Waverly Café in Waverly, TN shows a scrumptious quiche. Schatar debuts her cookbook, Gretchen talks chicken salad, and in Nashville, the Country Music Capital of the World, Zoey makes chicken egg rolls. At the legendary Big Als Café, Big Al makes his Adobe Chicken.

imdb.plot outline: Poultry Princess the series features delicious recipes with chicken, turkey, eggs, and other tasty poultry. Hosted by American Actress and Producer Schatar Sapphira Collier best known for attempting to cook - or rather to not cook - a raw chicken in the microwave as seen on Vh1. Guest Tele-chefs share their favorite dishes directly from their own kitchens with recipes real families can try at home.
